      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Combining alcohol with zolpidem can significantly increase the risk of serious side effects, including respiratory depression, which can be life-threatening. Even a small glass of wine with your medication can have an unpredictable and potentially dangerous impact on your body's ability to process both substances. It is highly recommended to solely rely on your prescribed medication and lifestyle changes for managing your sleep. If you continue to have difficulties, speak with your healthcare provider for safe alternatives, not alcohol.",
